</node>
<node id="&quot;TESSITURA&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Tessitura is the range of notes a singer can comfortably sing without strain."&lt;SEP&gt;"Tessitura is the range within which a piece of music is most frequently sung, often used to describe the typical range of a vocal type."</data>
