  <data key="d2">chunk-38fe20529f06a57ccfeaaae9d98d311a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BARI-TENOR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ROLE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bari-Tenor is a modern music theater voice type that requires versatility across high and low vocal ranges, including falsetto, belt, and a quasi-classical sound."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-38fe20529f06a57ccfeaaae9d98d311a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MIX/BELT SINGING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNIQUE"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Mix/Belt Singing is a technique that combines elements of both classical and popular singing styles, allowing for a wide vocal range."&lt;SEP&gt;"Mix/Belt Singing is a vocal technique that combines elements of head and chest voice, allowing for a wide vocal range and versatile sound."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-38fe20529f06a57ccfeaaae9d98d311a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9f8d4f36fdbe16d064eced5c8cb5bf54</data>
