<node id="&quot;TAXING AUTHORITY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Taxing Authority refers to government bodies responsible for collecting taxes and enforcing tax laws."&lt;SEP&gt;"Taxing Authority refers to the governmental bodies responsible for collecting taxes from the Company and its Subsidiaries."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 20}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAUSES OF ACTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Causes of Action are legal proceedings or claims that could affect the Company or its Subsidiaries, particularly in relation to taxes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENCUMBRANCES FOR TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Encumbrances for Taxes refer to any liens or claims on the assets of the Company or its Subsidiaries related to unpaid taxes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MATERIAL TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Material Taxes refer to significant tax obligations that the Company and its Subsidiaries must manage and pay."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GAAP&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"STANDARD"</data>
  <data key="d1">"GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which are the rules that dictate how financial statements should be prepared and presented."&lt;SEP&gt;"GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which are the standards for financial reporting and accounting practices."&lt;SEP&gt;"GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which dictate how financial statements should be prepared and reported."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 20}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TIMELY PAYMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Timely Payment refers to the timely payment of all registration, maintenance, renewal, and filing fees required for the Company Registered Intellectual Property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Timely payment refers to the requirement to pay taxes and other financial obligations within the specified deadlines."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8300f5060c70067c2752417b5bf332bf</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 24}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WRITTEN NOTICE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Written notice refers to formal notifications regarding potential tax issues or legal actions."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PENDING EXAMINATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Pending examinations refer to ongoing tax audits or reviews by Taxing Authorities."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PROPOSED ADJUSTMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Proposed adjustments refer to suggested changes in tax calculations or assessments by Taxing Authorities."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PROPERLY COMPLETED&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Properly completed refers to the accurate and timely filing of necessary tax forms and documents."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;TIMELY FILED&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Timely filed refers to the requirement to file tax forms and documents within the specified timeframes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ENCUMBRANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Encumbrances refer to any liens or claims on assets, including those related to unpaid taxes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Encumbrances refer to any limitations or restrictions on the Company Intellectual Property, excluding Permitted Encumbrances."&lt;SEP&gt;"Encumbrances refer to financial obligations or liens on assets, particularly for taxes or governmental charges."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8300f5060c70067c2752417b5bf332bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2e0437d914b81ea285bd3bc465ed2ef</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 24}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;APPROPRIATE PROCEEDINGS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Appropriate proceedings refer to legal actions taken to contest or resolve tax-related issues."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 21}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 49}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ROBERT PAINE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Robert Paine is a newly appointed assistant professor of zoology at the University of Washington in Seattle."&lt;SEP&gt;"Robert Paine is the ecologist who conducted the starfish removal experiment at Mukkaw Bay, born and raised in Cambridge, Massachusetts."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-486d8eb40e67b6566b8b345d6a8462d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2e0437d914b81ea285bd3bc465ed2ef</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;UNIVERSITY OF WASHINGTON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"University of Washington is an educational institution where Robert Paine works as an assistant professor."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-c2e0437d914b81ea285bd3bc465ed2ef</data>
</node>
