<node id="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"VALID AND ENFORCEABLE NON-DISCLOSURE AND CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENTS"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Debtors are aware of the existence of Company Intellectual Property and the measures taken to protect it, including non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors are aware of the existence of valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements, which are part of the company's measures to protect its intellectual property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors are parties involved in a debt-related agreement, likely referring to the Company or its subsidiaries."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to the individuals or entities that have knowledge of the status of the Company Registered Intellectual Property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to the parties involved in the debt-related transactions or disputes mentioned in the context."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors refer to the parties that owe money or obligations to the company."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4aabc09c64711d4a541ee30edcd7daaf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8300f5060c70067c2752417b5bf332bf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 2}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 23}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 51}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LABOR MATTERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Labor Matters refer to issues related to labor relations, employment, and compliance with labor laws."</data>
