<node id="&quot;LABOR UNION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Labor Union is an organization representing workers' interests and negotiating with employers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Labor union is an organization of workers formed to protect and further their interests, often through collective bargaining."</data>
