<node id="&quot;LABOR ARBITRATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Labor Arbitration is a process for resolving labor disputes through a neutral third party."&lt;SEP&gt;"Labor Arbitration is a process where a neutral third party makes a binding decision on a labor dispute."</data>
