<node id="&quot;LAWS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Laws are legal regulations governing the exchange of information and the rights of the Supporting Lenders and the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Laws are legal regulations or statutes that govern the actions of the Company and the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Laws refer to legal regulations and statutes governing labor, employment, and environmental practices."&lt;SEP&gt;"Laws refer to legal requirements and regulations that must be followed during the transactions."</data>
