<node id="&quot;SPRING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TIME"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Spring is a season when temperatures rise and flowers bloom, often triggering swarming behavior in bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Spring is the season when beekeepers often start new colonies and encourage swarming."&lt;SEP&gt;"Spring is the season when beekeepers often start new colonies and encourage swarming.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Spring is the season when bees are set out and hives are managed, requiring careful consideration of environmental factors."&lt;SEP&gt;"Spring is the season when new colonies are formed."</data>
