</node>
<node id="&quot;QUEEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Queen is a female bee that lays eggs and is crucial for the colony's survival and growth, especially during the period before and after swarming."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the female bee that lays eggs and is the leader of the Colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the reproductive female of the colony, responsible for laying eggs and maintaining the genetic diversity of the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Queen is the reproductive female bee in the hive, crucial for the survival and growth of the colony."</data>
