  <data key="d0">"ACTIVITY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Entering into agreements with Taxing Authorities involves formal contracts or arrangements to address tax liabilities and returns, including specific agreements like closing agreements under Code Section 7121."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CLOSING AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"AGREEMENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Closing agreement is a specific type of agreement under Code Section 7121 that resolves disputes between the IRS and taxpayers regarding tax liabilities."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;INTERNAL REVENUE CODE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOCUMENT"</data>
