  <data key="d0">"PERSON WHO CONTRIBUTED TO THE DEVELOPMENT OR CREATION OF ANY MATERIAL COMPANY INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Debtors are aware of the existence of valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements, which are part of the company's measures to protect its intellectual property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements are part of the company's measures to protect its intellectual property and ensure the confidentiality of trade secrets."&lt;SEP&gt;"Valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements are signed by individuals who contributed to the development or creation of material Company Intellectual Property to ensure the protection of the intellectual property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements are signed by individuals who contributed to the development or creation of material Company Intellectual Property to ensure the protection of the trade secrets."&lt;SEP&gt;"Valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements are specific types of agreements that ensure the protection of trade secrets and other confidential information."&lt;SEP&gt;"Valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements help protect trade secrets by ensuring that sensitive information is not disclosed to unauthorized parties."</data>
