</node>
<node id="&quot;SPECIAL MUSCLES FUNCTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FUNCTION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Special muscles, such as the diaphragm and intercostal muscles, serve specific functions in breathing."</data>
