</node>
<node id="&quot;DARWIN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Darwin is a renowned biologist who recognized the limitations on population growth and understood the work of Reverend Thomas Malthus."&lt;SEP&gt;"Darwin is a renowned naturalist who contributed significantly to the understanding of evolution but did not pursue the questions about 'bounds' set for different creatures."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-feb346664b4d17cc7509908b0f3a47ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b3ce1353c879e903a8fc9e1194706f7</data>
