</node>
<node id="&quot;GEOMETRICAL RATIO&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Geometrical ratio refers to exponential growth, which is mentioned as a characteristic of unchecked population growth."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-feb346664b4d17cc7509908b0f3a47ec</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MILLIONS OF WORLDS IN THE COURSE OF A FEW THOUSAND YEARS&quot;">
