  <data key="d6">chunk-fe239287d5735b89f51e1b54e606f90b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;ORDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Governmental Entity can issue Orders based on compliance with Environmental Laws."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-fe239287d5735b89f51e1b54e606f90b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must provide information to Governmental Entities to comply with antitrust laws."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company may submit filings or written materials to Governmental Entities, which may require review and consultation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc4be754ab02233d9e6804456be8d754</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;PARTIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">23.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Parties must cooperate with Governmental Entities in filings and submissions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Parties must submit to background checks and respond to requests from Governmental Entities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4399a6044c475cc6817f92d0cda2f1af</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;THE COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must comply with Governmental Entities in filings and submissions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company must submit to background checks and respond to requests from Governmental Entities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4399a6044c475cc6817f92d0cda2f1af</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">43.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must also comply with Governmental Entities in filings and submissions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders must also provide information to Governmental Entities to comply with antitrust laws."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders must also submit to background checks and respond to requests from Governmental Entities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4399a6044c475cc6817f92d0cda2f1af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Affiliates must provide information to Governmental Entities as part of the overall transaction requirements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Governmental Entities regulate the Transactions and require compliance with antitrust laws."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">83.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company and its Subsidiaries are involved in the transactions and must provide information."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company and its Subsidiaries employ individuals, indicating a hierarchical structure within the organization."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are part of the Company and must also comply with the same regulations and policies as the main Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries share the same intellectual property rights as the main company, ensuring consistent business practices and operations."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company acknowledges having had an opportunity to conduct due diligence on the Subsidiaries of the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries are related as parent and subsidiary organizations, both subject to the same compliance and warranty requirements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;21 U.S.C. § 335A&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must ensure that none of its officers, employees, or agents have been convicted of crimes that could lead to debarment under this legal section."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SOCIAL SECURITY ACT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must ensure that none of its officers, employees, or agents have been convicted of crimes that could lead to exclusion from federal health care programs under this act."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;U.S. DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES OFFICE OF INSPECTOR GENERAL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must not be a party to a Corporate Integrity Agreement with this office, indicating compliance with regulations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;56 FED. REG. 46191&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must comply with the policy respecting fraud and other illegal activities as outlined in this regulatory document."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;FRAUD, UNTRUE STATEMENTS OF MATERIAL FACTS, BRIBERY, AND ILLEGAL GRATUITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must avoid engaging in these illegal activities to avoid invoking the policy respecting them."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;CORPORATE INTEGRITY AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company must not enter into a Corporate Integrity Agreement with the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services Office of Inspector General to maintain compliance."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;PRODUCT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">34.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company sells Products and must ensure compliance with all applicable regulations for these Products."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company sells Products, which are subject to compliance and warranty provisions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;CONTRACTUAL COMMITMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company adheres to Contractual Commitments for its Products."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries must comply with all applicable contractual commitments for each Product they sell."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">152.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company and Supporting Lenders are involved in the same transactions and must provide information to each other."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company provides a list of employees to Supporting Lenders, indicating a formal relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are making representations and warranties to the Company as part of an agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are making representations and warranties to the Company as part of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are providing support or funding to the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders have the authority to execute agreements and documents related to the Restructuring process, which requires Company's Bankruptcy Court approvals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders provide financial support to the Company, which may involve reviewing information related to the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders receive a list of employees from the Company, suggesting a financial or contractual relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company acknowledges having had an opportunity to conduct due diligence on the Supporting Lenders and their Subsidiaries."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and Supporting Lenders are involved in an Agreement, implying a business relationship."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company does not rely on any written or oral statements, representations, promises, warranties, or guarantees from the Supporting Lenders or their Subsidiaries or Affiliates."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is receiving representations and warranties from the Supporting Lenders as part of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company provides standard warranty terms to Supporting Lenders, who receive this information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6e594c09c6de0c01da248106da72ab77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc4be754ab02233d9e6804456be8d754&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e52c63f43f0f8ca942825a1048d86e1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
