<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;MAINTAIN THE INSURANCE POLICIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Maintain the Insurance Policies involves the ongoing management of insurance coverage."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-abb871b166a3aa65b01cb9385e5352b5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;RENEW OR REPLACE THE INSURANCE POLICIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Renew or replace the Insurance Policies involves the continuation or updating of insurance coverage."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-abb871b166a3aa65b01cb9385e5352b5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;EXCEPT AS REQUIRED&quot;">
  <data key="d4">4.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Except as required involves actions that are not mandatory under certain conditions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-abb871b166a3aa65b01cb9385e5352b5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;TERMS OF ANY DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Terms of any Debtor Plan involve the specific conditions of the debt management plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-abb871b166a3aa65b01cb9385e5352b5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;THE APPROVED KEIP&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Approved KEIP involves the approved plan for incentivizing key employees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-abb871b166a3aa65b01cb9385e5352b5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;THE APPROVED DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">5.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Approved DEBTOR PLAN involves the approved plan for handling the company's debts and obligations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-abb871b166a3aa65b01cb9385e5352b5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;OFFICER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Officers are high-level executives within the Company, responsible for overseeing various aspects of the company’s operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;WORKS COUNCIL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A works council may represent employees in matters concerning their working conditions and relations with management within the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY DISCLOSURE LETTER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company Disclosure Letter contains detailed information about the Company and its operations, which is important for legal agreements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-22412b45b094ae4cf10a2ee87add10b3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">17.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is a party to the Agreement, indicating a formal business arrangement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is bound by the terms and conditions of the Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6e594c09c6de0c01da248106da72ab77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">32.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Affiliates are related to the Company, contributing to its operations and activities."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company and its Affiliates are part of the same organization and must share information."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company acknowledges having had an opportunity to conduct due diligence on the Affiliates of the Supporting Lenders."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc4be754ab02233d9e6804456be8d754&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company provides representations and warranties to itself regarding the completeness of information provided in connection with the transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DUE DILIGENCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company acknowledges having had an opportunity to conduct due diligence on the Supporting Lenders and their Subsidiaries."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company is involved in the Transactions and must provide updates and documents related to these transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is involved in the transactions contemplated by the Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company provides Representations and Warranties to itself regarding the completeness of information provided in connection with the transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;INFORMATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company relies on the information provided in connection with the transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSACTIONS CONTEMPLATED HEREBY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is a party to the transactions contemplated hereby."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;INFORMATION PROVIDED IN CONNECTION THEREWITH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company is responsible for the completeness of the information provided in connection with the transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;PETITION DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company initiates the Restructuring process by filing for Bankruptcy Court approvals starting from the Petition Date."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-e52c63f43f0f8ca942825a1048d86e1e</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;ORDER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Orders could potentially affect the validity or enforceability of the company's intellectual property, impacting its business operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The company and its subsidiaries own or have the right to use intellectual property that is essential for their business operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">25.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company operates the Business, which includes its activities and affiliates."&lt;SEP&gt;"The company conducts its business operations using its intellectual property, which is protected from infringement and violation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc4be754ab02233d9e6804456be8d754</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;PRODUCTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The company produces and sells products that rely on its intellectual property for protection and market differentiation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;JANUARY 1, 2017&quot;">
  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"January 1, 2017 marks the start of the period under review for any infringement, misappropriation, or violation of intellectual property rights."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;INFRINGEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The company must ensure that its intellectual property is not infringed upon by others."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;MISAPPROPRIATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The company must prevent its intellectual property from being misappropriated by others."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;VIOLATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The company must protect its intellectual property from being violated by others."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;CUSTOMERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Customers use the company's products, which rely on the company's intellectual property for protection and market differentiation."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPLIERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Suppliers provide raw materials or components that may involve the company's intellectual property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;CONTRACTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Contractors work under contract with the company, which may involve the use of the company's intellectual property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;VALUATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must redact valuation information to protect sensitive data."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;REDACTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company uses the process of redaction to protect sensitive information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;CONTRACTUAL ARRANGEMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must consider contractual arrangements when redacting information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;PRIVILEGE OR CONFIDENTIALITY CONCERNS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must address privilege or confidentiality concerns when redacting information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;OUTSIDE COUNSEL ONLY MATERIAL&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company designates some material as Outside Counsel Only Material."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;LAWS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must comply with Laws during the transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;WAITING PERIOD EXPIRATIONS OR TERMINATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must provide updates on Waiting Period Expirations or Terminations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;CONSENTS, CLEARANCES, WAIVERS, LICENSES, ORDERS, REGISTRATIONS, APPROVALS, PERMITS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must provide information on Consents, Clearances, Waivers, Licenses, Orders, Registrations, Approvals, Permits."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;PRODUCT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">36.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries sell Products and must also ensure compliance with all applicable regulations for these Products."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries sell Products, which are subject to compliance and warranty provisions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;CONTRACTUAL COMMITMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are part of the Company and must also comply with the same contractual commitments as the main Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-5042f28e2f78990ec882c0bc24a90328</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;TAX RETURNS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries prepare and file Tax Returns, which are required by law."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries owe Taxes, which must be paid according to legal requirements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9dec4a1a13d9fa1f25f4b96e1ac4a8a3</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;TAXING AUTHORITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also subject to tax-related actions and payments by the Taxing Authority."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;CAUSES OF ACTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also be involved in legal proceedings related to taxes, as indicated by the mention of pending Causes of Action."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;ENCUMBRANCES FOR TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries also have encumbrances for taxes on their assets, which must be managed according to legal requirements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL TAXES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also subject to material tax obligations that must be managed and paid."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;GAAP&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries must also adhere to GAAP principles when preparing and reporting financial statements, including tax-related information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;TIMELY PAYMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries must also ensure timely payment of taxes and other financial obligations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;WRITTEN NOTICE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also receive written notices regarding potential tax issues or legal actions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;PENDING EXAMINATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also be subject to pending tax examinations by Taxing Authorities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;PROPOSED ADJUSTMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also face proposed adjustments in tax calculations or assessments by Taxing Authorities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;PROPERLY COMPLETED&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries must also ensure that all necessary tax forms and documents are properly completed."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;TIMELY FILED&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries must also ensure that all necessary tax forms and documents are timely filed."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;ENCUMBRANCES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also have encumbrances on their assets related to unpaid taxes."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;APPROPRIATE PROCEEDINGS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also take appropriate legal proceedings to contest or resolve tax-related issues."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8a394556ccdea6653b1c8729f132928b</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also subject to the terms and conditions of the Debtor Plan, similar to the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;EFFECTIVE DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also bound by the Effective Date for the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;SEVERANCE PAY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are also responsible for providing severance pay to employees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL INCREASE IN SEVERANCE PAY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also provide a material increase in severance pay to employees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;ACCELERATE THE TIME OF PAYMENT OR VESTING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also accelerate the time of payment or vesting of certain benefits."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIALLY INCREASE THE AMOUNT OF COMPENSATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also materially increase the amount of compensation provided to employees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSFER OR SET ASIDE ANY ASSETS TO FUND ANY MATERIAL BENEFITS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also transfer or set aside assets to fund material benefits."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL LIABILITY UNDER ANY DEBTOR PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also incur material liabilities under the Debtor Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;LIMIT OR RESTRICT THE RIGHT TO MERGE, MATERIALLY AMEND, TERMINATE OR TRANSFER THE ASSETS OF ANY DEBTOR PLAN ON OR FOLLOWING THE EFFECTIVE DATE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also limit or restrict the right to merge, materially amend, terminate or transfer the assets of any Debtor Plan on or following the Effective Date."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;GROSS UP, INDEMNIFICATION, REIMBURSEMENT OR OTHER PAYMENT FOR ANY EXCISE OR ADDITIONAL TAXES, INTEREST OR PENALTIES INCURRED PURSUANT TO SECTION 409A OR SECTION 4999 OF THE CODE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also provide gross up, indemnification, reimbursement or other payment for any excise or additional taxes, interest or penalties incurred."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;FAILURE OF ANY PAYMENT TO BE DEDUCTIBLE UNDER SECTION 280G OF THE CODE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also face failure of any payment to be deductible under Section 280G of the Code."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;MAINTAIN OUTSIDE THE JURISDICTION OF THE UNITED STATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also maintain plans or agreements outside the jurisdiction of the United States."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;EMPLOYEES OR OTHER SERVICE PROVIDERS OF THE COMPANY OR ANY OF ITS SUBSIDIARIES WHO RESIDE OR WORK OUTSIDE OF THE UNITED STATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries may also employ individuals who reside or work outside the United States."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-913bc319974a823b4c2b9d601cf010c9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;UNITED STATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries have employees who reside or work outside of the United States, indicating global operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;COMPLIANCE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">36.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries also comply with all applicable labor, employment, and employment practices laws, indicating consistent adherence across the organization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;EMPLOYEES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">36.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries employ individuals, indicating a workforce relationship within the organization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;LABOR UNIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">28.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are not bound by any collective bargaining agreements or other agreements with labor unions, indicating no organized labor issues within the organization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;LABOR DISPUTES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">36.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries have no pending or threatened labor strikes, slowdowns, lockouts, or work stoppages, indicating stable labor relations within the organization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;THE COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Company and its Subsidiaries are interconnected organizations that collectively comply with labor and environmental laws."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-c485d67ace21ec2cbc0aea6458cb6703</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">36.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Subsidiaries are part of the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders and their Subsidiaries are involved in the transactions and must provide information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
