  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders are provided with information about the absence of labor grievances, indicating stable labor relations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ee24dc1f03c4e5fa6ed654495bb59d39</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">25.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders are also parties to the Agreement, indicating their involvement in the business arrangement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are parties to the agreement with the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-6e594c09c6de0c01da248106da72ab77&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">52.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Affiliates are part of the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders and Affiliates are related organizations involved in the transactions and filings."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders and Affiliates are related through the Company and must share information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4399a6044c475cc6817f92d0cda2f1af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">44.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders are also involved in the Transactions, which include filings and submissions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are involved in the Transactions and must provide updates and documents related to these transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are involved in the Transactions related to the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders are part of the transactions contemplated by the Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4399a6044c475cc6817f92d0cda2f1af&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e52c63f43f0f8ca942825a1048d86e1e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-50c13e3bb8e4150848f52b75b8673473&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-52ea1096ae3f4e248ede1dc1be934a73</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 6.1 QUALIFICATION; ORGANIZATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Section 6.1 Qualification; Organization outlines the requirements and current status of the Supporting Lenders."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;JURISDICTIONS THAT RECOGNIZE SUCH CONCEPT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must meet certain legal requirements in jurisdictions that recognize these concepts in order to be considered validly existing and in good standing."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;LEGAL ENTITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders are legal entities that are required to meet certain organizational and qualification requirements."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;DULY ORGANIZED&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must be duly organized according to the laws of their respective jurisdictions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;GOOD STANDING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must be in good standing in their jurisdictions of organization and in any jurisdiction where they conduct business."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;REQUISITE CORPORATE OR SIMILAR POWER AND AUTHORITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must have the requisite corporate or similar power and authority to own, lease, and operate their properties and assets, and to conduct their business as presently conducted."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;FOREIGN CORPORATION OR OTHER ENTITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must be qualified to do business and be in good standing as foreign corporations or other entities in each jurisdiction where the ownership, leasing, or operation of their assets or properties, or the conduct of their business requires such qualification."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL IMPAIRMENT OR MATERIAL DELAY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The failure to be in good standing or to have the requisite power and authority would not, individually or in the aggregate, materially impair or materially delay the Supporting Lenders' ability to perform their obligations under the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSACTIONS CONTEMPLATED HEREBY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are also parties to the transactions contemplated hereby."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;INFORMATION PROVIDED IN CONNECTION THEREWITH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders rely on the completeness of the information provided in connection with the transactions."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES OF THE SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are making the representations and warranties outlined in ARTICLE VI."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;QUALIFICATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must meet the qualifications outlined in Section 6.1 to be considered validly existing and in good standing."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;OPERATION OF ITS PROPERTIES AND ASSETS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must have the requisite power and authority to operate their properties and assets as part of their business operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;CONDUCT OF ITS BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must have the requisite power and authority to conduct their business as presently conducted."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;SEVERALLY AND NOT JOINTLY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Supporting Lender is individually responsible for their representations and warranties to the Company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;COLLECTIVE INTROSPECTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">24.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders engage in collective introspection about their role in the grand cosmic play."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;GRAND COSMIC PLAY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">24.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are part of a grand cosmic play that could rewrite human history."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;ENCRYPTED DIALOGUE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are using an encrypted dialogue to communicate sensitive information."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-ff621339cc48c1d0afec4e0b8efe1d64</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;" target="&quot;INTRA-TRANSACTIONAL COMMUNICATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
