  <data key="d4">34.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers manage the Hive, which is the center of all bee activities." )|&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeepers manage the Hive, which is the central location for all bee activities." )|&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeepers tend to hives and practice beekeeping."</data>
