  <data key="d4">38.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers manage honey bees and often attribute higher levels of intelligence to them, which is not accurate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeepers often attribute higher levels of intelligence to honey bees, which is not accurate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey bees are insects that react to specific stimuli based on their genetic programming and physiological development, which is often misunderstood by beekeepers."</data>
