<edge source="&quot;ORDER&quot;" target="&quot;INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Orders could affect the intellectual property rights of the company, impacting its business operations and product development."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;" target="&quot;BUSINESS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The business operations of the company and its subsidiaries depend on the protection and use of intellectual property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;" target="&quot;PRODUCTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Products are developed and protected using the company's intellectual property, ensuring market competitiveness."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-05c8b19983470d6fbb9ef38e0630e896</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRADE SECRETS&quot;" target="&quot;VALID AND ENFORCEABLE NON-DISCLOSURE AND CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements help protect trade secrets by ensuring that sensitive information is not disclosed to unauthorized parties."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4aabc09c64711d4a541ee30edcd7daaf</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRADE SECRETS&quot;" target="&quot;MATERIAL TRADE SECRETS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">40.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Material Trade Secrets are specific, valuable pieces of confidential information owned by the company."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4aabc09c64711d4a541ee30edcd7daaf</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;VALID AND ENFORCEABLE NON-DISCLOSURE AND CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENTS&quot;" target="&quot;PERSON WHO CONTRIBUTED TO THE DEVELOPMENT OR CREATION OF ANY MATERIAL COMPANY INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Individuals who contributed to the development or creation of material Company Intellectual Property are required to sign valid and enforceable non-disclosure and confidentiality agreements to protect the company's intellectual property."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4aabc09c64711d4a541ee30edcd7daaf</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;RESPIRATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">17.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The thorax is the primary site of respiration, where various muscles exert forces for breathing."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"The thorax, through its respiratory muscles, supports the process of respiration."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;VOICE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The thorax, through its respiratory muscles, supports the production of voice."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;ADAM'S APPLE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Adam's apple, a visible prominence in the neck, is associated with the larynx, which is located in the thorax."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;FOREIGN OBJECTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The thorax, including the larynx, protects the lungs from foreign objects."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;ABDOMINAL PRESSURE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The thorax, including the larynx, can contribute to increasing abdominal pressure for activities like lifting and childbirth."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;INHALATION POSTURE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The thorax, through its respiratory muscles, supports maintaining an inhalation posture during exhalation."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;EXHALATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">17.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Exhalation involves the compression of the Thorax to expel air from the lungs."&lt;SEP&gt;"The thorax, through its respiratory muscles, supports the process of exhalation."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-3fb90ae6bf97fbc21cb066ced098ee6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;THORAX&quot;" target="&quot;INHALATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">17.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Inhalation involves the enlargement of the Thorax to allow air to enter the lungs."&lt;SEP&gt;"The thorax, through its respiratory muscles, supports the process of inhalation."&lt;</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-3fb90ae6bf97fbc21cb066ced098ee6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dca9303a607f377e06cf6c0a4f271e11</data>
